dct_title_s: Map of Hutt Valley : and including Eastbourne, Upper Hutt, Wainuiomata
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Includes two ancillary maps to continue map. Includes "Locality diagram" and 1:10,000 enlargements of "Petone" and "Lower Hutt." Index on verso.
dct_creator_sm: New Zealand. Department of Lands and Survey
